Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.86,0:00:14.89,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.16,0:00:15.23,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.79,0:00:18.87,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:23.12,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:26.75,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.75,0:00:30.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.41,0:00:34.06,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.06,0:00:36.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.73,0:00:40.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.35,0:00:45.02,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:48.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:51.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.27,0:00:54.94,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:00:59.50,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.50,0:01:03.15,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.49,0:01:11.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:13.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.33,0:01:15.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.10,0:01:18.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:24.81,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,170.389)}The Monstrous Kamestone's
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:24.81,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,720.389)}Killer Aurora Plan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.06,0:01:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.92,0:01:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- What's going on?\N- I'm scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so creepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:01:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:02:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We came here to enjoy\Nourselves, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.79,0:02:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.81,0:02:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.58,0:02:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! An aurora!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.91,0:02:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's too strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.29,0:02:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,An aurora in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll take a picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.24,0:02:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My eyes... my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.18,0:02:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.28,0:02:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My eyes hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.44,0:02:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.96,0:02:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My eyes... my eyes hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They hurt! My eyes hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.01,0:02:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- My eyes hurt!\N- My eyes hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.40,0:02:44.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The appearance of\Nthe terrifying aurora
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:49.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,brought the wail of police and\Nambulance sirens all over Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.22,0:02:53.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The blinded townspeople were taken\Nto hospitals one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.80,0:02:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly! The third building.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Shimizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.63,0:02:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.60,0:02:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Their eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.68,0:03:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Their vision will\Nrecover, won't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.66,0:03:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We're doing everything\Nwe can to help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.63,0:03:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I can say for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't be blinded for\Nlife, will they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.90,0:03:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That aurora destroyed\Nthe patients' retinas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that an IV of a drug I've\Nbeen researching will cure them,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.65,0:03:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't be sure just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.69,0:03:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.14,0:03:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to find out\Nwhat caused that aurora.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a man-made\Nbeam of some kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone must be controlling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.23,0:03:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard Goro, Emi,\Nand the others were taken in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Hayato and Mr. Taki?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed that you\Nrecognized us, Goro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.32,0:03:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.44,0:03:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Chairman!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.52,0:03:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your eyes hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.79,0:03:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The pain's all gone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.24,0:04:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone got the\Nproper treatment
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,so no one is going to go blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.79,0:04:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.92,0:04:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But who would do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.79,0:04:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Your attempts at treatment\Nare all too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The cyborg I created\Npersonally...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All who witness the aurora\Ncreated by that cyborg
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,will rot from their eyes out
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,until their entire\Nbody dissolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.18,0:04:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the city of Tokyo\Nwill belong to Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.30,0:04:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Accursed Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.74,0:04:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what are they\Nplanning this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.03,0:05:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Put on the special eyeglasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker cyborg!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the one\Nbehind the auroras?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.52,0:05:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite an enchanting\Naurora, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.90,0:05:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki.\NDon't lose your eyeglasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You Shocker fiends...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You've really gotten\Nme mad this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.42,0:06:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh, I'm gonna fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.64,0:06:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.39,0:06:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Blasted Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Close off the emergency exits,\Nand stand by inside the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.30,0:07:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.82,0:07:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Can't see now, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.21,0:07:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Filthy Kamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.80,0:07:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, die in agony!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.64,0:07:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.62,0:07:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You requested aid\Nfrom FBI headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.52,0:07:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:07:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The resources of the\NTokyo Police and JSDF
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:08:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,are all focused on the\Nblinded townspeople.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And Hayato's lost his\Nsight, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I reckon that you and I are the\Nonly ones who can fight Shocker now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.62,0:08:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought stalling their momentum\Nwould be our best shot right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Fair point...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So, who are they sending?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanaka Robert.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.09,0:08:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,An FBI veteran,\Nthe son of Japanese immigrants.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the only person I can think of who\Ncan fight on even footing with Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Great to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When's he reaching Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He arrives tomorrow\Nmorning at eight o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The FBI says he's on\Nthe plane already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.22,0:08:42.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile,\Nthe passenger plane carrying
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.09,0:08:45.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Tanaka Robert was entering\NJapanese airspace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.94,0:08:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider is Shocker's\Nmost urgent concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.65,0:09:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless we destroy\Nthe Kamen Rider,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.32,0:09:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Operation: Blindness will\Nsurely end in failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.88,0:09:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Work with Kamestone to\Nsee the Kamen Rider dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All is proceeding\Nas I planned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd be\Narriving in Haneda.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.30,0:09:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to give\NShocker the slip.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How's Ichimonji doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.14,0:09:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He's completely blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.33,0:09:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's you\Nand me against Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The chief was worried,\Nso he gave me some special eye medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.57,0:09:45.55,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs50}Johoku Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.18,0:09:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for lights out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.30,0:09:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We ask that all our\Npatients now go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.86,0:10:05.31,Italics,,0,0,0,,Wretched Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:09.03,Italics,,0,0,0,,Even if I can't see,\NI'll still beat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Even blind,\NI'm still a cyborg...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I can drive using my\Nenhanced hearing alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:51.83,Italics,,0,0,0,,I drove.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:53.16,Italics,,0,0,0,,I drove!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:54.18,Italics,,0,0,0,,I was able to drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:57.40,Italics,,0,0,0,,Wretched Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:10:59.50,Italics,,0,0,0,,You've failed in your plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:01.74,Italics,,0,0,0,,I can still fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:04.96,Italics,,0,0,0,,And I will foil your plans!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:06.98,Italics,,0,0,0,,That is my mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess there's a motorbike\Ngarage near the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.40,0:11:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They say you can hear engine\Nnoises outside at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.92,0:11:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro and Yuri heard them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I must have\Nbeen out like a light.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't hear a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, best to rest up while\Nyou're in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.88,0:12:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.11,0:12:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro, eh? You sound excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato, I can see again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.77,0:12:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah!\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of the medicine\Nthat Robert brought!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.82,0:12:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're using it too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.58,0:12:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we're going to be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Goro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.82,0:12:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,See you around!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.99,0:12:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.16,0:12:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't work on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.52,0:12:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't even used it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.79,0:12:55.58,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(311,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:57.21,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs60\an9}Johoku Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.77,0:13:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That Hayato...\Nhe's been driving around blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.45,0:13:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that water?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.96,0:13:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gasoline...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would dump gasoline here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not gasoline...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.26,0:14:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nitro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.66,0:14:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's trying to kill Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.71,0:14:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Robert's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:19.71,Sign,,0,0,0,,Johoku Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.29,0:14:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I ran an analysis\Nof the eye medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's far more effective than\Nthe one I was researching.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Has this medicine restored\Nsight to all the other patients?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji, what in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.52,0:15:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Robert!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's that Shocker\Nbase you mentioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.32,0:15:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.46,0:15:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, it's time for you to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Taki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.26,0:16:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he'd found\Na Shocker base.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He went with Robert\Njust a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.72,0:16:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.31,0:16:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Robert's behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops, there's a transmitter\Non my motorbike.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.84,0:16:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,See which way it went.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.09,0:16:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,North-northwest, 20 kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.19,0:16:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mukogaoka Amusement Park!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mukogaoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.99,0:17:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Robert!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.96,0:17:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, it took you long\Nenough to catch on...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.49,0:17:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.78,0:17:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you're dying anyway,\NI might as well tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.26,0:17:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my true form!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.33,0:17:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamestone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Robert?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Having a rest at the\Nbottom of the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,An eternal one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Take him away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:17:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.52,0:18:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Taki?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.90,0:18:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.14,0:18:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd come\Nhere, Ichimonji Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.51,0:19:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamestone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:33.64,Italics,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.64,0:19:36.47,Italics,,0,0,0,,My eyes... my eyes hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.04,0:19:38.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Exposure to Kamestone's aurora
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:41.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,had rendered Kamen\NRider completely blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.34,0:19:46.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And the pain in Rider's eyes\Nwas continuing to grow worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.94,0:19:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Such is my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.09,0:19:54.50,Italics,,0,0,0,,No... he's going to beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.12,0:20:22.68,Italics,,0,0,0,,Where is Kamestone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.35,0:20:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Your end is finally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.32,0:20:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? You can't follow my\Nmovements, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:50.90,Italics,,0,0,0,,I can't hear Kamestone\Nmove with all this noise...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.98,0:21:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.12,0:21:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he's doing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.22,0:21:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.17,0:21:29.84,Italics,,0,0,0,,I can hear his footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.01,0:21:32.08,Italics,,0,0,0,,He won't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.96,0:21:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.79,0:22:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.58,0:22:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider, have your eyes recovered?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.58,0:22:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They recovered the\Nmoment he fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.63,0:22:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.32,0:22:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No more auroras, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.47,0:22:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we're all safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.90,0:22:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider got\Nrid of Kamestone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.72,0:22:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wish I could've seen\Nhim beat the monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.46,0:22:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw, right, Hayato?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.97,0:22:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I was still\Nblind at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.99,0:22:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.10,0:22:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll be sure to win the upcoming\NSilver Race instead, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.02,0:22:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno if I can trust\Nyou, Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.61,0:22:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.03,0:23:01.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamestone, creator of the\Ndeadly auroras, was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.20,0:23:07.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Shocker would return again,\Ntheir desire for world conquest unquenched.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.93,0:23:10.51,Cont,,0,60,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:14.43,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.40,0:23:15.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.27,0:23:16.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the monstrous Unicornos.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.87,0:23:20.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This one-horned monster spits a white\Nfluid that turns humans to stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.12,0:23:22.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His deathmatch against the two\NRiders, Ichimonji Hayato
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.28,0:23:24.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and Hongo Takeshi,\Ntakes place in a limestone cavern.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.35,0:23:25.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week\Nfor more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:30.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "Rock Monster Unicornos\NVersus the Double Rider Kick."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.90,0:23:30.90,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscy80\fs125\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(467.167,730.389)}Rock Monster Unicornos\NVersus the Double Rider Kick
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.01,0:23:40.85,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.43,0:23:43.43,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.43,0:23:45.39,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.39,0:23:48.44,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.94,0:23:50.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.81,0:23:52.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.69,0:23:54.48,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.48,0:23:55.93,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.28,0:23:58.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.37,0:24:04.04,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.04,0:24:07.62,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.62,0:24:11.29,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.72,0:24:15.51,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The Monstrous Kamestone's\NKiller Aurora Plan